Let’s now consider a coarser demodulation, in which phase fidelity is not required for the full observation time. Instead, the observation is broken into discrete segments of coherence time Tcoh\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
